 aspect of our approach\nrepresents a great potential for the use of deep learning application for the\nanalysis of clinical ultrasound data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2020 16:33:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-05"}
