tic nuclei might be favoured as progenitor candidates\nof repeating FRBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2020 18:00:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2020 08:56:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
