etecting some hydride and hydroxyl cations in the\nCrab and diffuse cloud environment. Some transitions of these molecules are\nhighlighted for future astronomical detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Aug 2020 06:46:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 06:34:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
