 the findings we discovered can benefit app developers towards\nbalancing ad revenue and user experience while ensuring app reliability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Aug 2020 05:38:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-28"}
